textAfterTable: Highlights: Flagship of the Oceania fleet, this elegant ship offers incomparable luxury and accommodates only 684 lucky guests. The Grand Dining Room features superb Continental cuisine, Toscana serves authentic Tuscan fare; Polo Grill is the consummate classic steakhouse, while Terrace Café and Waves Grill offer exceptional choices in a more casual atmosphere. In addition to Canyon Ranch SpaClub and a state-of-the-art fitness center, Canyon Ranch menu selections are available in the Grand Dining Room and Terrace Cafe. Sink into a book in the English-inspired library, attend a winetasting or try your luck at the casino. Your Package Includes: Your package includes shipboard accommodations, ocean transportation, fabulous entertainment and daily activities, on-board meals and some beverages, port charges and more. It does not include shore excursions, personal expenses, gratuities, or alcoholic beverages. Government fees and taxes are not included. View more
